      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fort_Lee%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Fort Lee is part of the Washington‑Rochambeau Revolutionary Route, a National Historic Trail tracing Washington and Rochambeau’s march to New York.",
